commit.message:
Windows: place gdbus.exe in parent folder

Otherwise it can't find required .dll files.

CI: temporarily upgrade packages

Until GTK 4.14.1 is available in the image.
DOWNLOADS.md: add third-party macOS packages

Fix translation files not being installed in some cases

This worked on accident before due to our i18n test.
Stop using legacy setuptools build backend

Revert "Stop using legacy setuptools build backend"

This reverts commit 23190ca0a0a2bb94990cbc4c9024b91d872bb99e.

Stop using legacy setuptools build backend

Refactor translation generation, since we can no longer import our
own packages.
downloads.py: remove redundant check

downloads.py: fix crash when no transfer is selected

Fixes #2961
transfers.py: fix typo

Broadway: hide main window controls

They are unnecessary in the web UI.
snapcraft.yaml: remove unnecessary Python packages

Debian: use gzip compression everywhere

We were mixing compression formats before (source tarball uses gzip,
everything else xz). In light of recent news, just use gzip for
everything.

search.py: don't update title too late

Third time's the charm...
appdata: add vcs-browser URL
search.py: update title after removing tab

Replace raster icons with vector icons

In light of the recent xz incident, I want to avoid unnecessary binary files
in the repository. While it's unlikely that anyone would attempt to include
payloads in our PNG files, there's no reason to use raster icons anymore.
search.py: remove window title notification when closing tab
tests: minor cleanups
tests: fix cleanup errors
